trans-unit.target: Expone los tipos <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem" /> a la automatización de la interfaz de usuario.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.GroupItemAutomationPeer" />.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.GroupItemAutomationPeer" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.GroupItemAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the control type for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.GroupItemAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el tipo de control correspondiente al control <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem" /> asociado a este objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.GroupItemAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of child elements of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.GroupItemAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene la colección de elementos secundarios del control <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem" /> asociado a este objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.GroupItemAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.GroupItemAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el nombre del control <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem" /> asociado a esta clase <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.GroupItemAutomationPeer" />.
Uno de los valores de enumeración.

trans-unit.source: Gets the control pattern for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.GroupItemAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el patrón de control para <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem" /> asociado a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.GroupItemAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: If <paramref name="pattern" /> is <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.ExpandCollapse" /> and the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.GroupItemAutomationPeer" /> contains an <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Expander" />, this method returns a reference to the current instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.GroupItemAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: Si <paramref name="pattern" /> es <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.ExpandCollapse" /> y el elemento <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.GroupItem" /> asociado a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.GroupItemAutomationPeer" /> contiene <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Expander" />, este método devuelve una referencia a la instancia actual de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.GroupItemAutomationPeer" />.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, this method calls the base implementation on <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElementAutomationPeer" /> which returns <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: En caso contrario, este método llama a la implementación base de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.UIElementAutomationPeer" /> que devuelve <see langword="null" />.
